\code{b12(Delta_j)} across the fixed target intervals
\code{Delta_j = j}, \code{j = 1, ..., delta_max}, and the two
autoregressive projection effects \code{b11(Delta_1)} and
\code{b22(Delta_1)} at the first target interval.
